wondershaper must be installed before hand 
this is just the tool to easily start and stop wondershaper

To Install Wonder Shaper

$ sudo apt install wondershaper 

$ cd bin
$ git clone https://github.com/magnific0/wondershaper.git
$ cd wondershaper
$ sudo make install


open wonder.py
set your port , download speed and upload speed 

port can be found using $ifconfig

Open terminal in the folder containing wonder.py or navigate to this file

$ python3 wonder.py [ run py file ]

Select the options to start or stop the wonderShaper

if you already started the process and want to modify the download speed or upload speed
use modify

set download speed and upload speed is for first time after that use modify alone
